{"title": "Catalanisme", "description": "\"Lo Catalanisme\" \u00e9s l\u2019obra de refer\u00e8ncia de Valent\u00ed Almirall i va suposar l\u2019arrencada del catalanisme pol\u00edtic o nacionalisme catal\u00e0 a finals del segle XIX. Partint de l\u2019an\u00e0lisi de pa\u00efsos com els Estats Units o Su\u00efssa, la seva proposta era, des de Catalunya i amb el concepte de \"particularisme\", influir en el conjunt d\u2019Espanya per descentralitzar el pa\u00eds i convertir-lo en una federaci\u00f3 d\u2019entitats equivalents i for\u00e7a aut\u00f2nomes. Va influir enormement en els personatges i les forces pol\u00edtiques que van liderar el catalanisme durant les primeres d\u00e8cades del segle XX, malgrat aquestes forces eren conservadores i no van seguir els seus postulats federals d\u2019esquerres.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\"Lo Catalanisme\" is the reference work of Valent\u00ed Almirall and marked the beginning of political Catalanism or Catalan nationalism at the end of the 19th century. Based on the analysis of the political systems of countries such as the United States or Switzerland, his proposal was, from Catalonia and with the concept of \"particularism\", to influence the whole of Spain to decentralize the country and turn it into a federation of equivalent and fairly autonomous entities. He greatly influenced the figures and political forces that led Catalanism during the first decades of the twentieth century, although these forces were conservative and did not follow their leftish federal postulates. (Introducci\u00f3n por Josep Maria Camps Collet)", "duration": 35337, "language": "Catalan", "authors": [{"id": "16321", "name": "Valent\u00ed Almirall i Llozer"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/catalanisme_2110.jpg", "copyright_year": "1886", "genres": ["Political Science"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Josep Maria Camps Collet"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Josep Maria Camps Collet"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Kazbek"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Pr\u00f2leg", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_00_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 286}, {"section": 1, "title": "Estat actual de la naci\u00f3 espanyola", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_01_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1364}, {"section": 2, "title": "Lo car\u00e1cter castell\u00e1", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_02_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2852}, {"section": 3, "title": "Lo car\u00e1cter catal\u00e1", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_03_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 3128}, {"section": 4, "title": "Lo Renaixement", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_04_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1671}, {"section": 5, "title": "Agravis y reclamacions", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_05_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 3006}, {"section": 6, "title": "Fonaments cient\u00edfichs del particularisme. Generalitats", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_06_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1515}, {"section": 7, "title": "Tendencia cient\u00edfica actual", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_07_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1114}, {"section": 8, "title": "La llibertat", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanisme_08_almirall_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1940}, {"section": 9, "title": "La igualtat", "readers": [16533], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/locatalanisme_2110_librivox/locatalanis